appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
+ TOURNAMENT MODE! First of its kind "Sentence-like user interface" makes even complex 3-period tournament time controls as easy to set up as it is to say it! Tournament mode also disables all phone functions per FIDE and USCF rules
+ GAME-SPECIFIC QUICK SETTINGS.
+ BYO-YOMI timing for Go & Shogi!
+ AUDIBLE COUNTING FOR GO in 8 languages!
+ BIG DELAY-TIME DISPLAY
+ Expanded help section (Not that you'll need it. But it's there.)
+ Ready to Stream! Killer OBS feature for YouTubers and Twitchers.

title: Tempest Game Clock

creator: Tempo Games LLC
descriptionHtml:
This is a COMPANION APP to the Tempest Game Clock (available at tempestclock.com)

A unique, tournament-style heavy-weighted game clock that uses your own android phone as its high definition, full color display. This app is intended only for owners of the Tempest Game Clock: a deluxe heavy-weighted, traditional form factor chess clock (using a patented precision rocker controller during play, not the touch screen). It pairs with this app to deliver clear analog and digital game timing with or without increments, delays, sudden death or OT time controls. Perfect for Chess, Backgammon, Go, Scrabble, Othello/Reversi, Checkers/Draughts, and other board games.

Tempest features a strict TOURNAMENT MODE - which disables all phone / text functionality during rated games per FIDE and USCF guidelines.

To see the clock in action and to order yours, please visit tempestclock.com.
descriptionShort: This is a COMPANION APP to the Tempest Clock (sold separately).

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Full Public Release version 1.0!
+ TOURNAMENT MODE strictly enforces airplane mode: no data/calls/text possible during play per FIDE and USCF rules.
+ Complex TOURNAMENT TIME CONTROLS made easy with Tournament Mode: simply Set it as you'd Say it! eg. "40 moves in 2h then 20 moves in 1h, then rest in 30 min." is not only how you'd describe the last FIDE world championships, but also this is exactly how you set Tempest. Simple.
+ Audible time countdowns available in 8 languages.
